 content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can update a shape source by setting its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","role":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"}}}